statements.sql: select count(*) as aggregate from `products` inner join (select `product_id`, sum(quantity) as quantity from `t_stocks` group by `product_id` having `quantity` > 1) as `stock` on `products`.`id` = `stock`.`product_id` inner join `shops` on `products`.`shop_id` = `shops`.`id` inner join `secondary_categories` on `products`.`secondary_category_id` = `secondary_categories`.`id` inner join `images` as `image1` on `products`.`image1` = `image1`.`id` inner join `images` as `image2` on `products`.`image2` = `image2`.`id` inner join `images` as `image3` on `products`.`image3` = `image3`.`id` inner join `images` as `image4` on `products`.`image4` = `image4`.`id` where `shops`.`is_selling` = 1 and `products`.`is_selling` = 1 and `secondary_category_id` = '2' and `products`.`name` like '%田中%'
